{"word":"οἰνιστήρια 1","slug":"οἰνιστήρια 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n72481\" key=\"oi)nisth/ria1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οἰν-ιστήρια</orth> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἱερά</foreign>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>, festival at which Athenians cut off the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μαλλός, κόννος</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σκόλλυς</foreign> of their sons previous to their being enrolled among the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔφηβοι,</foreign> at the same time offering <sense id=\"n72481.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a measure of wine</tr_> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">οἴνου μέτρον</etym>) to Heracles, and drinking part of it to the health of their <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φράτερες,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0461.tlg001:135\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eup.\">Eup.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">135</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phot.</author> </bibl> (<orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">οἰνιαστήρια</orth> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:907:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">907.18</biblScope> </bibl>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}